    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and grate (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot </strong>to a large bowl with your <strong>free range</strong> <strong>chicken thighs</strong>, <strong>cumin seeds</strong>,<strong> ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the<strong> grated garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>",
