    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your sandwich, fill the <strong>crusty ciabatta</strong> with the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>free range chicken thigh souvlaki</strong>,<strong> </strong>a<strong> </strong>dollop of<strong> tzatziki</strong>, a couple of <strong>herby fries </strong>and a <strong>tomato round </strong>– this is your <strong>free range chicken thigh souvlaki sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>remaining herby fries</strong> to the side with the <strong>remaining free range chicken thigh souvlaki skewer</strong>,<strong> remaining tomato rounds</strong>,<strong> sliced cucumber </strong>and<strong> reserved chopped mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
